netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain

Class DomainAvailabilityPrice

  • java.lang.Object
    • netistrar.clientapi.objects.domain.DomainAvailabilityPrice

  • public class DomainAvailabilityPrice
extends java.lang.Object
    Domain Availability Price objects are returned as part of the DomainAvailability object structure. They encode the price for an operation (registration, renewal, transfer) for a domain name for a number of years. The pricing fields returned will vary depending upon the price type (standard / premium) and whether or not the pricing is a hint derived from the Netistrar pricing cache or confirmed pricing derived from a call to the getLiveDomainAvailability within the Netistrar Domain Availability API.
